These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, tea
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person drinking juice is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking cola is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Beverage    | cola    | tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, drama, spy
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person watching drama movies is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | drama     | animation        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, epic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre         | epic     | adventure | zombie |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, disco, gospel
1. the person watching sports movies is the fan of disco##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Music-Genre         | punk  | disco | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
3 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the fish##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Pet   | ferret | hedgehog     | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, water
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| Beverage   | water     | lemonade    | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, october
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Birthday           | july         | september         | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, august
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person who's birthday is in july##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Birthday   | february | august | july |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Flower         | azalea | amaryllis | daffodil |

