.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the australian is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Birthday     | january     | november   | february        |

