The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the photographer##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the security-guard##1
3. the photographer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Job   | photographer  | teacher | security-guard   |
