.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different games are played: billiard, snooker, bridge
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Game      | billiard | snooker | bridge |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

