.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, art-deco
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| House     | wooden  | art-deco   | gothic-revival |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 